{"title":"钢与火的韵律（二首）","authors":["聂鑫森"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":11,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢与火的韵律（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"聂鑫森"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我拾起一颗小小的螺钉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上班喧响的人影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剪裁出早晨的风景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳在肩的林莽上跃动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偶尔一低头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见了一颗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被昨天遗忘的螺丝钉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拨开揶揄的目光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我拾起了它"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓起腮帮，吹去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它身上的风尘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后，用一团棉纱擦呀擦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亮得像一颗星星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它是被颠簸的岁月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毫不足惜地丢弃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是在匆忙的急转弯中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失去自己的重心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我找到了太阳的一个焦点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早晨的一个投影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工厂的一个憧憬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我深知它在生活中的位置"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"懂得它理想的旋纹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它需要新的吻合"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的拧紧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，我拾起了一颗小小的螺钉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领工装"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的个子有些稚嫩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领工装时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却高喊一声：我要大号"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我留下那么多空间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让每一块肌腱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在钢与火的拚搏中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去适应力的扩张与呼啸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让一条条汗水的河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映着蓝色的云块"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢乐地奔跑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我会变得健壮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会长大、长高"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像钢，像火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奏响生命奔腾不息的音乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，青春的岁月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凸出遒劲的线条"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是钢的雕塑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是火的素描"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国工人的履历表"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工装是蓝色的封面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"题目是印在上面的工号"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：株洲市《株洲日报》）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}